               <floruit notBefore="1959" notAfter="1987">He was a prominent Amharic writer. 
                  He received his elementary education
                  in <placeName ref="LOC3577Gondar"/>, then graduated from <placeName ref="LOC1216AddisA"/> 
                  Technical School in <date>1956/57</date> 
                  specializing in radio mechanics. 
                  But he left his field of specialization and turned to journalism, 
                  made swift progress from a curb reporter up to the editor in chief until <date>1966/67</date>. 
                  He authored novels and plays. 
               </floruit>
